descriptions.ban: This will permanently bans a user from the guild with the reason provided.
descriptions.botinvite: Users can use this as an easy utility to invite bots to their servers, or yours if you allow it.
descriptions.sinvite: Generates an instant invite to your guild.
descriptions.kick: Kicks the mentioned user from the guild with the reason provided.
descriptions.lockdown: Temporarily lock any channel from interaction from other users.
descriptions.mcstatus: Display information about a Minecraft Server.
descriptions.poll: Make a poll with a question with thumbs up and down reactions.
descriptions.purge: This allows messages to be deleted from a channel.
descriptions.report: Report a player to the staff of this Discord server.
descriptions.role: This will add or remove a role from the mentioned user.
descriptions.say: This will send a message as the bot on your behalf.
descriptions.shutdown: This will shutdown the bot instance on all Discord servers.
descriptions.tag: This allows you top create nice tags to add to your messaging experience.
descriptions.terminate: Will make the bot leave the Discord guild and terminate it's instance.
descriptions.tweet: Tweet from your Discord client to a Twitter account (if enabled & configured).
descriptions.unban: This will unban a user from the guild with the reason provided.
descriptions.userinfo: Displays information about the mentioned user.
descriptions.warn: This command is used to warn people.
descriptions.warnlevel: This command gives the information about the Warning Level of a user.
descriptions.prefix: Allows you to change the prefix in your guild.
descriptions.coins: Shows how many coins you have.
descriptions.cmdp: Shows the permissions for the moderation commands.
descriptions.pussy: Generates a img of a pussy.
descriptions.avatar: Generates an embed with the avatar of the tagged user.
descriptions.ball: Gives the answer for something you say.

permissions.missingAdmin: Please make sure that you have the`MANAGE_GUILD` permission.
permissions.missingMod: Please make sure that you have the `MANAGE_GUILD` permission.
permissions.missingChannel: Please make sure that the server has the `aduit-log` and `reports` channel for the bot working correctly.
